<sec id="id-8ba08cc7-033b-44d3-82f7-af9b8a762aad"><title><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="3466e2d3-64cc-4202-916d-1f3084808eca" timestamp="1656534385135"?><bold><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3466e2d3-64cc-4202-916d-1f3084808eca"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="da721bb3-84e7-47c0-d3ee-041bd2e68e69" timestamp="1671534843742"?>Plan, Do, Check and Act<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="da721bb3-84e7-47c0-d3ee-041bd2e68e69"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="22fd6e44-0a89-4d1d-dec5-dcc93b164972" timestamp="1656534385135"?></bold><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="22fd6e44-0a89-4d1d-dec5-dcc93b164972"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="58ec1690-d4e4-4888-d268-d743a553588c" text="Include the initiative in the organization’s social responsibility policy" timestamp="1671534843742"?></title><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="dbec9374-9533-4779-dab2-d4481e588db0" text="Special internal and external events can be organized, such as workshops dedicated to the subject.In addition, the organization can publish external communication materials based on, for example, information on the commitments made by the organization.Posters, videos, exhibitions, card games and board games can also be used and distributed. Media and formats used for dissemination should be accessible for all.Providing information on the initiative to prevent sexual and gender-based violence allows it to be included in the organization’s social responsibility policy. Internal tools can be used to communicate this information, such as the organization’s rules and regulations, which contain the articles of law and the sanctions, the welcome handbook, which explains the policy on the prevention of sexual and gender-based violence, internal memos, the intranet site, etc." timestamp="1671534851199"?></sec>